item.dc:creator: @Not_Pwnd Not Pwnd
item.description:
@Not_Pwnd wrote:

Of course it is. If you are just starting out, then it won’t be easy. You need common sense, and you have to read the code inside.

addItem(itemID, 1); would at the itemID of the item (anyone you put there…) to your inventory.
sendMessage(“put your message here”); would send a player the message ‘put your message here’

You’ll have to write your own skills. It’s pretty complicated.
